---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "About Us";
const lang = "en";
---

<Layout title={title} lang={lang}>
  <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 prose prose-lg prose-blue max-w-none">
    
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About HLH Mulbadaw Ltd</h1>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Our Foundation</h2>
      <p>
        Established in 2006, The Farm (HLH Mulbadaw Ltd) is a commercial, non-profit company 
        guided by the core value: <strong>"Working together for His Praise and Glory."</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        Our existence is intrinsically linked to the <em>"Foundation Friends of Haydom" (FOH)</em>, 
        headquartered in Mandal, Norway. FOH serves as our de facto owner, ensuring that our 
        commercial activities directly support the <strong>Haydom Lutheran Hospital (HLH)</strong> 
        in Tanzania.
      </p>
    </section>
    <br>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Mission and Objectives</h2>
      <p>The mission of The Mulbadaw Farm is to operate a profitable, sustainable mixed-farming 
        enterprise that acts as a resource for healthcare and development. Our primary goals include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Increasing food production through sustainable agricultural methods.</li>
        <li>Creating local jobs and promoting employment.</li>
        <li>Facilitating research and education in collaboration with local and international institutions.</li>
        <li>Providing economic support to Haydom Lutheran Hospital.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <br>
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Our Values</h2>
      <p>We are grounded in Christian heritage and traditions, prioritizing respect for human 
        dignity and the natural environment. We manage our estate according to Christian ethics, 
        emphasizing three pillars:</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 font-bold text-yellow-700">
        <span>Honesty</span> | <span>Respect</span> | <span>Transparency</span>
      </div>
    </section>
<br>
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Guidelines and Commitment</h2>
      <p>Our management approach is defined by a commitment to the local community and 
        environmental stewardship:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Sustainable Management:</strong> We utilize responsible management across cultivated, grazing, and forest areas.</li>
        <li><strong>Community Focus:</strong> We emphasize methods adaptable to small- and medium-scale farmers.</li>
        <li><strong>Inclusivity:</strong> We value the skills of our staff, fostering an environment of responsibility and ownership.</li>
        <li><strong>Environmental Responsibility:</strong> Through diversified practices, we strive to minimize our carbon footprint and combat the effects of climate change.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </article>
</Layout>